        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段偏軟 恒指跌227點報22716點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段向下，恒生指數開市報22716點，跌227點或0.99%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5617點，跌61點或1.08%；國企指數以8390點開市，跌72點或0.86%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/791x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250212_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/791x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250212_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地媒體引述美團(03690)官方公眾號公布指，集團將逐步為全職及穩定兼職騎手繳納社保；美團ADR昨晚已受壓，股份今早在港開報158元，挫5.78%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他重磅股亦跌多升少，今日將公布季度業績的阿里巴巴(09988)開報122.4元，1.37%；同在今早派成績表的嗶哩嗶哩(09626)也跌3.36%，報158元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：嗶哩嗶哩官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/11/bplib_20230713-104754_source-web_嗶哩嗶哩-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：嗶哩嗶哩官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/11/bplib_20230713-104754_source-web_嗶哩嗶哩-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：嗶哩嗶哩官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他重磅股亦跌多升少，騰訊(00700)跌1.33%，開報491.2元；京東(09618)開報153.8元，跌0.26%；小米(01810)企穩49.45元開市，暫時無升跌。滙控(00005)昨天再創3年高位後，今早開報87.6元，跌0.91%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14719456-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c227%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b122716%e9%bb%9e",
